OL,3,CMaternity unit may reopen in stages,
OL,4,Csay NHS bosses
OL,6,FYeovil Hospital's maternity unit may
OL,7,Freopen in stages rather than all at
OL,8,Fonce, senior NHS staff have confirmed.
OL,10,FThe Somerset NHS Foundation Trust
OL,11,Ftemporarily closed the special care
OL,12,Fbaby unit and inpatient maternity
OL,13,Fservice at Yeovil Hospital on May 19
OL,14,F2025, due to concerns about "the
OL,15,Fsafety, quality and fragility of the
OL,16,Fpaediatric service" on the site.
