OL,3,CMaternity unit may reopen in stages,
OL,4,Csay NHS bosses
OL,6,FThe closure of the units came
OL,7,Ffollowing a 2024 Care Quality
OL,8,FCommission report, which rated
OL,9,Fmaternity services in Somerset,
OL,10,Fincluding those at Yeovil District
OL,11,FHospital, "inadequate".
OL,13,FThe report found the unit at Yeovil
OL,14,FDistrict Hospital did not have enough
OL,15,Femergency equipment to care for babies
OL,16,Fsafely and didn't always have enough
OL,17,Fmedical staff.
