OL,6,FIt also found that some staff failed
OL,7,Fto follow infection control
OL,8,Fprinciples, like washing their hands
OL,9,Fbefore administering care.
OL,11,FThe trust announced in mid-October
OL,12,Fthat it intended to reopen the
OL,13,Ffacilities on April 21, 2026,
OL,14,Ffollowing a successful period of
OL,15,Frecruitment and other changes being
OL,16,Fput in place.
