OL,3,CMaternity unit may reopen in stages,
OL,4,Csay NHS bosses
OL,6,FBut senior officers say they are
OL,7,Funable to confirm whether the entire
OL,8,Ffacility will reopen on the same day
OL,9,For whether a "graded" approach will be
OL,10,Ftaken to ensure staff and patient
OL,11,Fsafety.
OL,13,FSally Bryant, the trust's director of
OL,14,Fmidwifery, said: "We're keeping a
OL,15,Ffocus on improvement, and that's
OL,16,Fworking really well at the moment.
OL,18,F"We continue to evaluate the maternity
OL,19,Ftriage service to make sure it's where
OL,20,Fit needs to be."
