OL,3,CMaternity unit may reopen in stages,
OL,4,Csay NHS bosses
OL,6,FSince the closure was implemented, 453
OL,7,Fbabies have been delivered that would
OL,8,Fotherwise have been born at Yeovil.
OL,10,FOf these, 215 were born at Dorset
OL,11,FCounty Hospital in Dorchester, 178 at
OL,12,FMusgrove Park Hospital in Taunton, 31
OL,13,Fwere home births and 29 were at other
OL,14,Fhospitals including Royal United
OL,15,FHospital in Bath.
