OL,3,CMaternity unit may reopen in stages,
OL,4,Csay NHS bosses
OL,6,FSince the closure, numerous changes
OL,7,Fhave been implemented within the
OL,8,Fmaternity unit, including installing
OL,9,Fnew fire doors, upgrading the
OL,10,Felectricity supply to the unit and
OL,11,Fredecorating with "refreshing decor"
OL,12,Fand new art murals.
OL,14,FAdditional support has been provided
OL,15,Fto the most vulnerable expectant
OL,16,Fparents, with resources being
OL,17,Fcommitted to support "displaced
OL,18,Ffamilies" who are now accessing
OL,19,Fservices at Dorchester or Taunton.
