OL,3,CMaternity unit may reopen in stages,
OL,4,Csay NHS bosses
OL,6,FWhen asked if all of Yeovil's
OL,7,Fmaternity facilities would feasibly be
OL,8,Fable to open in one fell swoop, Ms
OL,9,FBryant said: "I wish there was an easy
OL,10,Fanswer.
OL,12,F"That is a question that we're trying
OL,13,Fto answer that for ourselves. Because
OL,14,Fwe support and advocate women having
OL,15,Fchoice, some people who may have been
OL,16,Fon the traditional Yeovil pathway may
OL,17,Fsay 'I've had some of my care at
OL,18,FDorchester or Musgrove, and therefore
OL,19,FI would like to stay there for my
OL,20,Fbirth'.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
