OL,3,CMaternity unit may reopen in stages,
OL,4,Csay NHS bosses
OL,6,F"We don't yet know what people might
OL,7,Fchoose, so we're working through what
OL,8,Foptions we do have at our disposal.
OL,10,F"There are risks around all of those
OL,11,Foptions, but what I would say is that
OL,12,Fwe are working towards to a full
OL,13,Freopening ` that is our ambition."
OL,15,FThere was also concerns around staff
OL,16,Fupheaval, however, Ms Bryant assured
OL,17,Fthat there has not been an increase in
OL,18,Fthe normal turnover of staff at the
OL,19,Ffacility during the closure.
